messages.text: What areas are you working on?
Hey Dasha, it's amazing to see how your work with CastingForm is revolutionizing talent representation in Hollywood—congrats on all your success!
Hey Michael, it's impressive to see how you're pioneering in venture capital with MDSV Capital and your continued impact on early-stage startups!
Hey Thomas, it's impressive to see how you're driving AI innovation and fostering global connections through the Transatlantic AI eXchange and your advisory roles!
Hey Josephine, it's awesome to see how you're helping artists connect directly with their fans at Medallion—keep up the great work!
Hey Greg, it's impressive to see how you've combined your expertise in strategic alliances and marketing with your passion for education and non-profit work to make a real impact!
Hey Carlos, it's cool to see how you're helping entrepreneurs settle in Silicon Valley with Startup Embassy and sharing your experiences through your blog!
Hey Kushal, it's impressive to see how you're driving innovation at Xoxoday and supporting startups as an angel investor!
Hey Kae, it's awesome to see how you're bringing together great minds in Silicon Valley through your investment club and weekly engagements!
Hey Inna, just wanted to say I’m impressed by your diverse HR experience and your knack for driving successful projects in various roles!
Hey Oleg, I'm really impressed by your dedication to supporting early-stage entrepreneurs and your extensive experience in venture capital—keep up the great work!
